  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The intended use is pre-market submission support for a Class II spinal implant system, restricted to quasi-static axial compression-bending loading per ASTM F1717 protocol. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. Scope is limited to non-cannulated 7.5 mm titanium alloy constructs under ambient laboratory conditions.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-predicts-f1717-stiffness-and-yield-load",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/nagaraja-pedicle-screw-fea-ensemble-v2",
