      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver version control, regression testing suite, and documented QA procedures must be in place for all three FEA platforms (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes).",
      "rationale": "All three FEA platforms operate under ISO 9001-compliant quality management systems with documented version control and regression test suites. Achieved level exceeds the required level for this model risk classification."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
